What you need to know:  In women’s hockey, Kenya suffered another heavy loss as they lost 15-0 South Africa in their final Pool 'B' match at the University of Birmingham Sports Centre.In beach volleyball, Kenya’s pair of Gaudencia Makokha and Brackcides Agala face Ghanaians on Wednesday and will be looking to bounce back from their 2-0 (21-15, 21-5) loss at the hands of Canadian duo Saraha Pavan and Melissa Humana.